      <div class="bio__text" data-reveal>
        <p>
          I am a mixed-media artist creating textured artworks that bridge the gap between
          structure and fluid mediums.
        </p>
        <p>
          For the first part of my life, my world was defined by systems and structures in
          Germany. It was a predictable rhythm that kept me safe, but left little space for
          creativity. What began as a passion for surfing evolved into a whole new way of living:
          I left the landlocked lifestyle behind, moved abroad to the coast and allowed myself to
          be guided by creativity, freedom and flow.
        </p>
        <p class="bio__text-clear">
          Today, my art is the tangible map of that journey. By pairing raw textures with fluid
          resin, I capture the beautiful contradiction of life and the coast.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work is designed to bring the vibrant and grounding energy into my collectors homes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
